Package de.uniwue.zpd.dla.page.layout.converter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LayoutConverter
    Interface for converters that convert a page layout to comply with a certain format version.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChainConverter
    Meta converter representing a chain of converters.
    ConversionMessage
    Format conversion related message
    Converter_2009_03_16_to_2016_07_15
    Converter for 2013-07-15 format to 2016-07-15 format.

    Converts script values
    Converter_2010_01_12_to_2009_03_16
    Converter for 2010-01-12 format to 2009-03-16 format.

    Adds temp region if there is no region (at least one region required)
    Converter_2010_03_19_to_2010_01_12
    Converter for 2010-03-19 format to 2010-01-12 format.

    Removes unsupported text types (signature-mark, catch-word, marginalia, footnote, footnote-continued, TOC-entry)
    Converter_2013_07_15_to_2010_03_19
    Converter for 2013-07-15 format to 2010-03-19 format.

    Removes unsupported graphic types (frame, barcode, decoration) Removes unsupported text types (endnote, other) Removes unsupported colours (other) Removes unsupported languages Converts unsupported regions to 'Unknown' (Music, Chem, Advert) Removes unsupported attributes from regions, lines, words, and glyphs
    Converter_2013_07_15_to_2016_07_15
    Converter for 2013-07-15 format to 2016-07-15 format.

    Converts script values
    Converter_2016_07_15_to_2013_07_15
    Converter for 2016-07-15 format to 2013-07-15 format.

    Removes unsupported graphic types (frame, barcode, decoration) Removes unsupported text types (endnote, other) Removes unsupported colours (other) Removes unsupported languages Converts unsupported regions to 'Unknown' (Music, Chem, Advert) Removes unsupported attributes from regions, lines, words, and glyphs
    Converter_2016_07_15_to_2017_07_15
    Converter for 2016-07-15 format to 2017-07-15 format.

    Converts script values
    Converter_2017_07_15_to_2016_07_15
    Converter for 2017-07-15 format to 2016-07-15 format.

    Removes unsupported graphic types (frame, barcode, decoration) Removes unsupported text types (endnote, other) Removes unsupported colours (other) Removes unsupported languages Converts unsupported regions to 'Unknown' (Music, Chem, Advert) Removes unsupported attributes from regions, lines, words, and glyphs
    Converter_2017_07_15_to_2018_07_15
    Converter for 2017-07-15 format to 2018-07-15 format.
    Converter_2018_07_15_to_2017_07_15
    Converter for 2018-07-15 format to 2017-07-15 format.
